title: Jamie O'Hara kicked out of Celebrity Big Brother in shock secret eviction
text:
GONE: Jamie O'Hara has reportedly been evicted from Celebrity Big Brother 
The footballer has been given the boot just days before the final on Friday night. 
The 30-year-old was up for eviction alongside Calum Best, Kim Woodburn, Nicola McLean and Jedward. 
Jamie got a similar deal to Jasmine Waltz who was sent home without a live eviction, and had to leave via the backdoor, according to The Sun Online. 
CHANNEL 5 SHOWMANCE: Jamie has been getting very close to Bianca CBB's sexiest housemates The sexiest ever Celebrity Big Brother housemates. Who's top of your list? 1 / 60 “Love is a strong word but I love everything about you” Jamie O'Hara 
The dad of three had been enjoying a flirtationship with Bianca Gascoigne, even sharing a number of kisses in the house. 
But he'd been left upset and annoyed when it came out that the blonde bombshell actually had a boyfriend on the outside. 
It's safe to say it was her man, CJ Meeks, who was most upset as he was seen looking devastated while reading about the CBB romance. 
Jamie seemed to have fallen head over heels for Bianca, telling her: "Love is a strong word but I love everything about you.
